PN,30901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FNew guidance on single-sex spaces
OL,8,Fcould mean that disabled and trans
OL,9,Fpeople will have to "compete" for
OL,10,Faccess to toilets, campaigners and
OL,11,Fgovernment analysis has warned.
OL,13,FUpdated guidance from Britain's rights
OL,14,Fwatchdog the Equality and Human Rights
OL,15,FCommission (EHRC) confirmed that
OL,16,Fsingle-sex services must be on the
OL,17,Fbasis of biological sex.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThis means that a trans man (who is
OL,8,Fbiologically female) can be excluded
OL,9,Ffrom a male-only service, while a
OL,10,Ftrans woman (who is biologically male)
OL,11,Fcan be excluded from a female-only
OL,12,Fservice.
OL,14,FThe guidance applies to a wide range
OL,15,Fof facilities including hospitals,
OL,16,Fsports, leisure centres and cafes and
OL,17,Fstates that an accessible toilet could
OL,18,Fbe used as a mixed-sex toilet `
OL,19,Fprompting concerns among disabled
OL,20,Frights groups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThe Disabled People Against Cuts
OL,8,F(Dpac) national campaign group said
OL,9,Ftrans people using accessible toilets
OL,10,Fintended for use by disabled people is
OL,11,Fnot "an acceptable work around" and
OL,12,Fexpressed concerns that this will
OL,13,Fbecome the common approach by service
OL,14,Fproviders.
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,F"Opening the toilets up to another
OL,8,Fgroup of people will mean higher
OL,9,Fvolumes of traffic, potentially
OL,10,Fpreventing disabled people from
OL,11,Fmeeting our essential needs," said
OL,12,FEllen Clifford, a member of Dpac's
OL,13,Fnational steering group.
OL,15,F"Disabled people are still actively
OL,16,Fcampaigning for adequate access to
OL,17,Ftoilet facilities and this will create
OL,18,Fyet another barrier in our day-to-day
OL,19,Flives."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@]O]wD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FHowever, she added that Dpac also
OL,8,Fconsiders "the exclusion of trans
OL,9,Fpeople from single sex toilets to
OL,10,Frepresent discrimination" and that the
OL,11,Fnew guidance serves to "effectively
OL,12,Fpit against each other two of the most
OL,13,Fdiscriminated against groups in
OL,14,Fsociety and risk inflaming yet further
OL,15,Fan already unbearably contentious
OL,16,Fissue".
OL,26,@pD@KOUrD@YO]sD@XOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThe EHRC's new code for service
OL,8,Fproviders was published just over a
OL,9,Fyear after a landmark ruling by the
OL,10,FUK's highest court, which ruled that
OL,11,Fthe words "woman" and "sex" in the
OL,12,FEquality Act 2010 refer to a
OL,13,Fbiological woman and biological sex.
OL,15,FThis means that obtaining a gender
OL,16,Frecognition certificate does not
OL,17,Fchange your legal sex for Equality Act
OL,18,Fpurposes, although gender reassignment
OL,19,Fis still classed as a protected
OL,20,Fcharacteristic of its own.
OL,26,@sD@KOUsD@QO]sD@WOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FDespite this distinction, the guidance
OL,8,Fsays service providers should "monitor
OL,9,Fwhether there is any negative impact
OL,10,Fon both trans and disabled people and
OL,11,Ftake appropriate action".
OL,13,FThe guidance was published alongside
OL,14,Fan equality impact assessment, which
OL,15,Fstates that use of disabled toilets as
OL,16,Fa so-called third space by trans
OL,17,Fpeople who do not wish to use the
OL,18,Ftoilet of their biological sex "may
OL,19,Fnot foster good relations between
OL,20,Fgroups".
OL,26,@pD@_OUsD@XO]zD@`OU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,F"This is because disabled people and
OL,8,Ftrans people may have to compete to
OL,9,Faccess a limited number of
OL,10,Ffacilities," the Office for Equality
OL,11,Fand Opportunity (OEO) said.
OL,13,F"Disabled people have had (and
OL,14,Fcontinue) to fight for access to
OL,15,Fsuitable toilets.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@LO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,F"Whether this creates tension between
OL,8,Fthe two groups will depend on how
OL,9,Fproviders choose to arrange and label
OL,10,Ftheir facilities, which is likely to
OL,11,Fbe impacted by resources and site
OL,12,Flimitations."
OL,14,FWhat else is in the new guidance on
OL,15,Fsingle-sex spaces?
OL,17,FLike toilets, single-sex changing
OL,18,Frooms must be used on the basis of
OL,19,Fsomeone's biological sex rather than
OL,20,Fgender identity, the guidance says.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FIt also advises that mixed-sex
OL,8,Fchanging facilities which have private
OL,9,Fcubicles with floor-to-ceiling
OL,10,Flockable doors are likely to be
OL,11,F"proportionate and lawful" under the
OL,12,FEquality Act.
OL,14,FThe updated guidance states trans
OL,15,Fpeople should compete alongside others
OL,16,Fof their birth sex rather than gender
OL,17,Fidentity.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FSport England, which is an arms-length
OL,8,Fbody of government, said it is
OL,9,F"reading and reviewing" the code "and
OL,10,Fassessing the implications for both
OL,11,Fsport provision and facilities".
OL,13,FThe organisation said it will issue an
OL,14,Fupdate "in due course", but it is
OL,15,Fexpected that could be months from
OL,16,Fnow, as it will need to consult with
OL,17,Fother UK sporting bodies.
OL,19,FThe new code says that single-sex
OL,20,Fhospital wards can lawfully exclude
OL,21,Ftrans patients.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]qD@bOUsD@_O]vD@HOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThe code states that hospitals can
OL,8,Fchoose to provide a single-sex ward
OL,9,F"for women patients to protect their
OL,10,Fsafety, privacy and dignity", and that
OL,11,Fif they do, it has to be on the basis
OL,12,Fof the sex patients were assigned at
OL,13,Fbirth.
OL,15,FIn this scenario, trans patients would
OL,16,Fbe placed on a ward based on the sex
OL,17,Fthey were born as rather than the
OL,18,Fgender they identify as.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FUnder current NHS guidance, trans
OL,8,Fpatients can be accommodated on single-
OL,9,Fsex wards based on the gender they
OL,10,Fidentify as.
OL,12,FThe NHS has also said it will review
OL,13,Fthe updated code "with the aim of
OL,14,Fpublishing draft guidance for the
OL,15,Fhealth service shortly".
OL,17,FEHRC chairwoman Mary-Ann Stephenson
OL,18,Fsaid provision for a trans patient
OL,19,F"might be about individual rooms, it
OL,20,Fmight be about thinking about how you
OL,21,Forganise the ward".
OL,26,@uD@ROUwD@WO]{D@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FShe added: "The decisions that service
OL,8,Fproviders make in order to make sure
OL,9,Fthat services are both single-sex and
OL,10,Fthat there's provision for trans
OL,11,Fpeople will vary depending on the kind
OL,12,Fof organisation of facilities and what
OL,13,Fservice they're providing."
OL,15,FStephenson urged a "common sense
OL,16,Fapproach" to the guidance and has
OL,17,Frejected any notion of the policing of
OL,18,Ftoilets.
OL,26,@oD@LOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,F"We've had separate toilet services
OL,8,Ffor women and men for decades, and we
OL,9,Fdon't have people on the door checking
OL,10,Fwho goes in," she said.
OL,12,FThe code notes that it would be "very
OL,13,Funlikely to be proportionate to put a
OL,14,Ftrans person in a position where there
OL,15,Fis no service that they are allowed to
OL,16,Fuse".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@MO]tD@aOUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FFor Women Scotland, who brought the
OL,8,Fcase which resulted in the Supreme
OL,9,FCourt ruling last year, hailed the
OL,10,Fpublication of the long-awaited EHRC
OL,11,Fservice provider guidance as a
OL,12,F"significant milestone in ensuring
OL,13,Fwomen's rights are upheld and
OL,14,Fprotected".
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FThe group said the code's publication
OL,8,Fshould "mark an end to the unjustified
OL,9,Fexcuses and delays in implementing"
OL,10,Fthe court ruling, adding that there is
OL,11,F"now no reason for public bodies and
OL,12,Forganisations to evade their
OL,13,Fresponsibilities to women".
OL,15,FBut the Trans+ Solidarity Alliance
OL,16,Fargued the new code has an
OL,17,F"exclusionary core" and could risk
OL,18,F"pushing trans people yet further out
OL,19,Fof public life".
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@cO]sD@AOUuD@ZO]yD@AOUyD@SO]zD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FMeanwhile the president of the
OL,8,FNational Union of Students (NUS) said
OL,9,Fthe code "will functionally exclude
OL,10,Ftrans people from engaging in public
OL,11,Flife" and called for Parliament to
OL,12,Freject it.
OL,14,FThe code, which would apply across
OL,15,FEngland, Scotland and Wales has now
OL,16,Fbeen laid before Parliament for
OL,17,Fscrutiny from both MPs in the Commons
OL,18,Fand peers in the Lords and will not be
OL,19,Fenacted for 40 days.
OL,26,@qD@JOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779555957
OL,3,CSingle-sex space guidance 'risks
OL,4,Ctension between disabled and trans
OL,5,Cpeople'
OL,7,FWhile a vote would not be required to
OL,8,Fenact the code and make it statutory,
OL,9,Feither House could pass a motion to
OL,10,Freject it within that period.
OL,12,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,13,Four political experts are across all
OL,14,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,15,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
